description:
This Fractals Skill will give you the Guild Wars 2 Fractal name, and recommended Agony Resistance value.  
Just ask about a level number.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Fractals what is Level 19.
name: Fractals Info
shortDescription: Which Fractal is Level 47?  This is a quick reference to Guild Wars 2 Fractals by level, and includes the recommended agony resistance.
